+   * A graphical explanation of the touch data flow:
+   *
+   * +----------------------------+             +--------------------------------+
+   * | ResponderTouchHistoryStore |             |TouchHistoryMath                |
+   * +----------------------------+             +----------+---------------------+
+   * |Global store of touchHistory|             |Allocation-less math util       |
+   * |including activeness, start |             |on touch history (centroids     |
